Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.70,0:00:02.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Aaaah!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.76,0:00:05.38,McGonagal,,0,0,0,,Heavens to Betsy, what's all the hubbub-
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.86,0:00:07.98,McGonagal,,0,0,0,,Oh my. Not another one.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.98,0:00:09.61,Pomfrey,,0,0,0,,Oh dear me, it's Hannah Abbott.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.48,0:00:12.38,Pomfrey,,0,0,0,,Poor thing, she's been petrified!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.01,0:00:14.11,Pomfrey,,0,0,0,,Just like the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.95,0:00:16.61,Pomfrey,,0,0,0,,How many is that now, Headmaster?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.61,0:00:18.35,McGonagal,,0,0,0,,341...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.15,0:00:22.48,McGonagal,,0,0,0,,Now, I'll have to send word to the Ministry.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.48,0:00:25.18,McGonagal,,0,0,0,,The fate of the school is in their hands now.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.75,0:00:28.08,McGonagal,,0,0,0,,Well, take Miss Abbott to the \Ninfirmary. Spit spot!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.61,0:00:32.95,McGonagal,,0,0,0,,Attention Hogwarts Students!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.55,0:00:36.08,McGonagal,,0,0,0,,Hogwarts is no longer safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.28,0:00:38.88,McGonagal,,0,0,0,,There has been yet another petrification,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.04,0:00:45.41,McGonagal,,0,0,0,,Putting us over the allowed limit of 340 student casualties each school year.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.98,0:00:51.95,McGonagal,,0,0,0,,As a result, new safety regulations must be implemented immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.35,0:00:56.15,McGonagal,,0,0,0,,Students shall, henceforth, report directly to class from their dormitories.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.48,0:01:01.41,McGonagal,,0,0,0,,All lollygagging privileges all dismissed until further notice
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.81,0:01:02.78,McGonagal,,0,0,0,,Beware, Children.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.15,0:01:06.92,McGonagal,,0,0,0,,unless the Chamber is found, and the monster inside destroyed
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.18,0:01:09.56,McGonagal,,0,0,0,,The ministry may close the school
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.90,0:01:11.00,McGonagal,,0,0,0,,...forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.68,0:01:13.91,McGonagal,,0,0,0,,Wizard God, help us all.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.56,0:01:20.36,Luna,,0,0,0,,Close Hogwarts?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.88,0:01:22.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Forever?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.88,0:01:24.14,Neville,,0,0,0,,Oh d-d-dear.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.40,0:01:29.61,Seamus,,0,0,0,,You know, I heard all this wouldn't be a problem if the school's entire supply of Mandrakes didn't get destroyed
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.61,0:01:31.61,Seamus,,0,0,0,,when somebody mucked up the Herbology Room.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.08,0:01:35.22,Dean,,0,0,0,,Yeah, and it's too bad those were the last Mandrakes in the whole world.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.61,0:01:38.81,Dean,,0,0,0,,You know, Mandrake juice is the only thing that can cure being petrified.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.25,0:01:41.90,Luna,,0,0,0,,Or if somebody kills the Chamber of Secret's monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.28,0:01:44.11,Luna,,0,0,0,,That would break the petrification spell!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.31,0:01:46.11,Cho Chang,,0,0,0,,Yeah, but who's gonna do that, Looney?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.11,0:01:47.75,Seamus,,0,0,0,,You know whose fault all this is?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.22,0:01:49.14,Seamus,,0,0,0,,Harry Potter's.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.25,0:01:51.20,Seamus,,0,0,0,,I heard it was him that wrecked the greenhouse.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.31,0:01:54.81,Seamus,,0,0,0,,The school just blamed it on \Nsome Latina chick, cause they're racists.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.35,0:02:00.90,Seamus,,0,0,0,,But it was actually Harry that did it, and probably \Non purpose so as no one else could save the school.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.28,0:02:03.98,Seamus,,0,0,0,,Bloody darby, couldn't handle not being the hero for once.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.40,0:02:06.58,Seamus,,0,0,0,,Well, where are you now, Harry Potter?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.31,0:02:08.91,Seamus,,0,0,0,,Where are you now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.35,0:02:11.61,Ron,,0,0,0,,Shame on you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.21,0:02:12.51,Dean,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.58,0:02:16.51,Ron,,0,0,0,,I said, shame on you,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.56,0:02:17.86,Ron,,0,0,0,,Seamus!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.91,0:02:21.38,Ron,,0,0,0,,Shame on all of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.40,0:02:23.38,Ron,,0,0,0,,Look at yourselves!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.21,0:02:25.15,Ron,,0,0,0,,Sitting around,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.61,0:02:26.95,Ron,,0,0,0,,complaining,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.46,0:02:28.40,Ron,,0,0,0,,spreading gossip.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.40,0:02:32.24,Ron,,0,0,0,,Harry didn't destroy the Herbology Room.  \NIt was like that when he got there! \N
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.45,0:02:36.78,Ron,,0,0,0,,Do you guys wanna know why Harry always saves the school?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.88,0:02:40.36,Ron,,0,0,0,,Because he doesn't wait around for someone else to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.28,0:02:45.38,Ron,,0,0,0,,Do you remember our fourth year, when Igor Karkaroff was bewitching exchange students?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.78,0:02:50.01,Ron,,0,0,0,,Making them compete in the Tri-wizard tournament, not to be confused with the House Cup tournament.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.18,0:02:55.68,Ron,,0,0,0,,Who was it that unmasked Karkaroff as a Death Eater and sent him to Azkaban?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.48,0:02:57.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Harry.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.04,0:03:02.20,Ron,,0,0,0,,And - and - and - and - and Cho, what did you do that year?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.88,0:03:04.58,Cho Chang,,0,0,0,,Fooled around with Victor Krum.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.92,0:03:05.61,Lavender Brown,,0,0,0,,Me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.61,0:03:07.20,Seamus,,0,0,0,,Yeah, me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.95,0:03:09.20,Seamus,,0,0,0,,Shooting marbles.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.80,0:03:10.38,Seamus,,0,0,0,,Tag.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.35,0:03:13.88,Seamus,,0,0,0,,Ordering all them pizzas to Filch's office.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.14,0:03:15.81,Seamus,,0,0,0,,We did some right fooling around that year.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.84,0:03:17.62,Ron,,0,0,0,,Yeah, remember our fifth year,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.75,0:03:23.55,Ron,,0,0,0,,When Umbridge became the Minister of Magic and appointed those incestuous Carrow twins as the Dark Arts Teachers.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.55,0:03:27.85,Ron,,0,0,0,,Luna, what did you do when the Carrows told you to shoot the cruciatus curse at Neville?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.25,0:03:31.08,Luna,,0,0,0,,Ask if I could try the killing curse?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.56,0:03:36.28,Ron,,0,0,0,,And who was the only one of us who didn't raise his wand against a fellow student?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.08,0:03:37.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Harry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.91,0:03:42.32,Ron,,0,0,0,,And when the Carrows tried to torture the location of the DA out of Cho,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.32,0:03:45.95,Ron,,0,0,0,,who tricked them into walking through Devil's Snare where they were torn asunder?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.35,0:03:47.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Harry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.18,0:03:50.58,Ron,,0,0,0,,And then united the giants against Umbridge's evil ministry!? Who was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.82,0:03:51.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Harry!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.66,0:03:52.64,Ron,,0,0,0,,That's right. Harry!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.45,0:03:56.91,Ron,,0,0,0,,And how do you repay him, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.32,0:04:00.35,Ron,,0,0,0,,Tell him he stinks.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.05,0:04:03.68,Ron,,0,0,0,,We drive him away. Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.65,0:04:07.48,Ron,,0,0,0,,The school's in bigger trouble than ever now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.68,0:04:09.45,Ron,,0,0,0,,And I hope you're all proud of yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.10,0:04:12.31,Ron,,0,0,0,,Because the only person standing between you,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.78,0:04:14.45,Ron,,0,0,0,,and whatever's in that chamber of secrets,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.65,0:04:16.45,Ron,,0,0,0,,is your new headboy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.78,0:04:18.21,Ron,,0,0,0,,Malfoy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.18,0:04:25.75,Malfoy,,0,0,0,,Slow, slow, slow.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.35,0:04:28.65,Malfoy,,0,0,0,,Well, well, well,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.08,0:04:32.38,Malfoy,,0,0,0,,if it isn't the ignorant mob that handed me supreme power.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.38,0:04:36.58,Malfoy,,0,0,0,,They all look so tiny from up here. Don't they, Goyle?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.25,0:04:38.58,Goyle,,0,0,0,,Yes, me lord!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.35,0:04:48.58,Malfoy,,0,0,0,,Alright, The Head Boy Draco Malfoy will now hear your questions, \Nconcerns, praise, worship...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.64,0:04:50.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Rabble! Rabble! Rabble!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.12,0:04:51.60,Malfoy,,0,0,0,,Order!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.90,0:04:53.46,Malfoy,,0,0,0,,None of that sounded like worship
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.75,0:04:56.68,Dean,,0,0,0,,So what's your plan to save the school Malfoy?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.68,0:04:58.88,Dean,,0,0,0,,For dealing with this Chamber of \NSecrets thing?! \N
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.88,0:04:59.52,Malfoy,,0,0,0,,Plan?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.51,0:05:02.55,Malfoy,,0,0,0,,What do you mean plan?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.01,0:05:06.34,Malfoy,,0,0,0,,I already have a four-step plan in place.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.00,0:05:07.51,Malfoy,,0,0,0,,One,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.95,0:05:09.64,Malfoy,,0,0,0,,Watch mudbloods get petrified.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.18,0:05:12.15,Malfoy,,0,0,0,,Two. Laugh. Repeat.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.25,0:05:19.82,Malfoy,,0,0,0,,And I promise, that my administration will do all it can to ensure we aid this Heir of Slytherin hero!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.98,0:05:23.48,Malfoy,,0,0,0,,Draco Malfoy will bring change you can believe in!\N
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.66,0:05:25.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Booo!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.48,0:05:26.11,Malfoy,,0,0,0,,Silence.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.91,0:05:28.21,Malfoy,,0,0,0,,Silence you worms!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.68,0:05:30.95,Malfoy,,0,0,0,,I wish you had one neck, I'd hack it through!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.54,0:05:35.08,Malfoy,,0,0,0,, Now, I may not be as deft of politician as that Fozzy Bear.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.35,0:05:37.38,Malfoy,,0,0,0,,But I think we can all agree,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.51,0:05:40.64,Malfoy,,0,0,0,,that I fill the position much better than that Harry Potter ever could.
